For Tim:

0. cd mesa
1. Bump the version in VERSION
2. Update/finalise the release notes
3. Build a temporary tarball and check the scons build
cd mesa && mkdir foo && cd foo && ../autogen.sh && make dist
tar -xaf mesa-*xz && cd mesa-* && scons
4. Release
./modular/release.sh . --dry-run
5. Check your write access for uploading the tarballs
ssh annarchy.freedesktop.org mkdir -p /srv/ftp.freedesktop.org/pub/mesa/test123
ssh annarchy.freedesktop.org rm -r /srv/ftp.freedesktop.org/pub/mesa/test123
